Content.Name: Classes
Content.Title: Spring and Summer Classes
Content.Abstract: Spring and Summer session offers another option for PMP students. It has multiple options including the following classes: Foundations Religion (FDREL 130) - Mission Preparation, Foundations Cultural Awareness (FDINT 201) - Global Hotspot: Pakistan, Communications 175 (COMM 175) - Communication Essentials, Spanish (SPAN 101) - Beginning Spanish 1, Foundations Religion (FDREL 121P) - Book of Mormon for Pre-missionaries, Foundations Cultural Awareness (FDHUM 105) - Humanities, and General Studies (GS 101) - Principles of Personal Achievement.
